data.description: Beautiful one-owner two story home with double front porches. True 4 bedroom. Recent updates include: new roof, interior paint, carpet and floor coverings in upstairs baths, new deck and garbage disposal. Large owner's suite with spacious walk-in closet opens onto a private Charleston-style balcony. Garden tub and stand-up shower in primary bathroom with double vanity. All 4 bedrooms have walk-in closets. Large backyard is fenced and backs up to peaceful nature preserve giving total privacy behind. This lovely neighborhood is immaculate and convenient to all of Lexington's amenities as well as interstates.
